North Hills Electronics Incsaid its North Hills Israel Ltd unit received a commitment for1,500,000 dlrs in financing from the &lt;Overseas PrivatePlacement Corp>.    The company said the money will be used to construct andequip a 14,000-square-foot manufacturing plant in Israel.    North Hills said construction of the plant, which will makeelectronic power supplies and interconnect devices for computerlocal area networks, will be completed by the second quarter ofits current fiscal year. Reuter&#3;